{"meta":{"title":"終結官商勾結獨裁，南非公民社會的反擊","site_name":"NGO 推進器","site_img":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/dc/Atul_Gupta_protest_banner_-_Cape_Town_Zuma_must_fall.jpg/800px-Atul_Gupta_protest_banner_-_Cape_Town_Zuma_must_fall.jpg","subtitle":"Story of the river and its gorge","author":"jxtsai","keywords":"Gradac, Storyteller, Sourcefabric","rsspingback":"http://medium.twngo.xyz","description":"測試 mural 說故事多媒體製作工具","src":"https://s3.eu-central-1.amazonaws.com/muralsoftware/test_stories/spring_sample_story/index.html","share":false,"facebook":false,"twitter":true},"items":[{"textcentred":{"id":"0","title":"前言","files":["","","","",""],"subtitle":"<p>2018年2月南非總統 Jacob Zuma 宣佈辭職<br></p>","intro":"<p>此一政治事件背後南非近廿年來政治、社會的變動胍絡，且試圖用 <a href=\"https://getmural.io/\" target=\"_blank\">Mural </a>新聞專題故事軟體來作簡單介紹呈現。<br></p>","snippets":[{"align":"center","title":"","src":"uploads/default/mural.svg","credits":"","text":"<p><br></p>"}]}},{"textcentred":{"id":"1","title":"從種族鬥爭到階級鬥爭","files":["","","","","","",""],"subtitle":"<p>1994年新南非成立後，政府迅速頒發了一個對人權具有高度保護的憲法。然而，時至今日，發展的福祉不但遠未惠及全民，各種不公正現象更是屢禁不止，由不平等和不公正造成的社會動盪，政治暗殺和警察暴力愈演愈烈。<br></p>","intro":"<p><br></p><p><br></p>","snippets":[{"align":"right","title":"","src":"https://img2.jiemian.com/101/original/20171224/151405980513424400_a580xH.jpg","credits":"","text":"<p>九十年代初南非種族隔離制度解體，黑人的政治勢力得到空前的整合，形成了與白人政府進行談判以求權力和平過渡的基本政治條件。然而所謂的談判，只是精英階層之間，廣大民眾不可能具有這種高度複雜的政治和經濟斡旋的能力，於是隨後建立的彩虹國雖然在初期普遍反映了黑人大眾的集體利益，但馬上就主要服務於黑人中產階級的政治和經濟欲求。</p><p><br></p>"},{"align":"left","title":"","src":"https://img3.jiemian.com/101/original/20171224/151405983324819400_a580xH.jpg","credits":"","text":"<p>所以九十年代的改革談判實情是白人政權在岌岌可危的壓力下，將大量的政治和經濟權力讓渡給黑人精英，同時，要求上台的黑人精英保護白人的既得經濟利益。新南非之新，核心只是實現了白人精英和黑人精英聯手控制社會財富的分配和再分配。南非近五年連續被聯合國評為世界貧富差距最大的國家。貧富差距的加大不可避免地使新南非變成黑人精英爾虞我詐，爭權奪利的舞台，使得國內政治日趨腐敗和階級矛盾日趨擴大。</p><div><br></div>"}]}},{"slideshowhorizontal":{"id":"2","title":"利用左右方的 < > 觀看不同的照片","images":[{"title":"利用左右方的 < > 觀看不同的照片","credits":"","srcphone":"https://khanyajournal.org.za/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/22.jpg","srcmedium":"https://khanyajournal.org.za/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/22.jpg","srcmain":"https://khanyajournal.org.za/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/22.jpg"},{"title":" Marikana Massacre ","credits":"","srcphone":"https://www.groundup.org.za/media/_versions/images/photographers/Ihsaan%20Haffejee/Marikana-20170817/MARIKANA%20MEMORIAL%20IH%202_extra_large.JPG","srcmedium":"https://www.groundup.org.za/media/_versions/images/photographers/Ihsaan%20Haffejee/Marikana-20170817/MARIKANA%20MEMORIAL%20IH%202_extra_large.JPG","srcmain":"https://www.groundup.org.za/media/_versions/images/photographers/Ihsaan%20Haffejee/Marikana-20170817/MARIKANA%20MEMORIAL%20IH%202_extra_large.JPG"},{"title":" Marikana Massacre ","credits":"","srcphone":"https://cms.qz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/safrica-lonmin.jpg","srcmedium":"https://cms.qz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/safrica-lonmin.jpg","srcmain":"https://cms.qz.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/safrica-lonmin.jpg"}],"files":["","","","","","","","",""]}},{"slideshowvertical":{"id":"3","title":"上下移動的靜態照片 ","images":[{"title":"","credits":"","srcphone":"uploads/default/50f7b2e5aa8dc1b863bb9f339625d096.jpg","srcmedium":"uploads/default/50f7b2e5aa8dc1b863bb9f339625d096.jpg","srcmain":"uploads/default/50f7b2e5aa8dc1b863bb9f339625d096.jpg"}],"files":["","",""]}},{"imagebackground":{"id":"4","format":{"fullpage":false},"title":"<p>激化的抗議&nbsp;</p>","subtitle":"<p>真正的運動鎮壓者卻可逍遙法外。今日南非的黑暗來自統治階級完全有能力將憲法和新聞玩弄於股掌之間。<br></p>","text":"<p>今日的南非，各種社會矛盾都處於不斷激化的狀態，祖馬政府的腐敗，種族情緒的對立，政商之勾結正將南非拖入一種極不穩定的狀態。</p><p>現在社會底層的許多抗議活動已有失控之勢，許多抗議者放棄正常的抗議渠道，採用更加激進的方式表達自己的利益訴求，這就不可避免地產生了許多不可控的暴力。</p><p>民眾為什麼傾向於採取冒險的行為來抗爭？原因在於舊有的渠道在很大程度上已經失效，下情不能上達，民眾只好揭竿而起。這種草根的抗議行動往往得不到媒體的客觀報導，而在審判的法庭上，被繩之以法的又總是抗議的民眾。&nbsp;<br></p>","image":{"srcmain":"http://an24.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/southy-pro.jpg","srcphone":"https://img3.jiemian.com/101/original/20171224/151405977696159600_a580xH.jpg","srcmedium":"https://img2.jiemian.com/101/original/20171224/151405986385356000_a580xH.jpg"},"audio":{"mp3":"uploads/default/South African National Anthem.mp3","ogg":""}}},{"textcentred":{"id":"5","title":"<p>總統的好朋友</p>","files":["","","","","","",""],"subtitle":"","intro":"<p>2016 南非監察辦公室（<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Public_Protector\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The Office of the Public Protector</a>）發佈 「掠奪之國（<a href=\"http://qz.com/825789/state-capture-jacob-zuma-the-guptas-and-corruption-in-south-africa/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">State of Capture</a>）」報告。該報告顯示，總統祖瑪（Jacob Zuma）允許住在南非的富裕印度古普塔家族－<a href=\"https://www.google.co.zm/url?sa=t&rct=j&q=&esrc=s&source=web&cd=2&cad=rja&uact=8&ved=0ahUKEwjc2vK53JPQAhXDXBQKHV4lBL4QFggbMAE&url=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FGupta_family&usg=AFQjCNGd_vJ3AGrx3pocOg3lPmzKiKwkOA&sig2=x81F3W5peHQAF6W2lkkmKQ&bvm=bv.137904068,d.d24\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Guptas</a> 使用公共資源圖利個人，並且影響重大政府決策。</p>","snippets":[{"align":"center","title":"","src":"https://globalvoices.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/statecapture-cover.jpg","credits":"","text":""},{"align":"right","title":",","src":"https://media.pri.org/s3fs-public/styles/story_main/public/photos/2013-May/south_africa_india_gupta_family_2013_05_02.jpg","credits":",","text":"<p>來自印度的古普塔三兄弟，1993年在種族隔離尚未完全結束之際便移民南非，在多年沉浮之後，他們押中了祖馬總統這塊寶。通過和祖瑪總統及其家族甚好的私交，Gupta 家族開始全面通過「吸血蟲」的形式，通過關係和不正當手段獲得大量政府項目的合同，將南非國家財政的公帑通過種種方式據為己有，大量鯨吞國有資產，而他們的同夥和「生意夥伴」就是這位南非總統和他的多名子女。<br></p>,後來，Gupta家族甚至擁有了在背後任命祖瑪內閣成員的生殺賞罰大權，一時間南非執政黨內，順古普塔者昌，逆古普塔者亡。在他們權利的巔峰時刻，連南非空軍的飛行基地，都可以成為他們女兒婚禮的私人飛機起降場所。"}]}},{"textcentred":{"id":"6","title":"<p>公民社會</p>","files":["","","","","","",""],"subtitle":"","intro":"","snippets":[{"align":"left","title":"","src":"https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/guptaleaksvideo.jpg","credits":"","text":"<p>南非強大的自由媒體和公民社會開始了他們的絕地反擊。南非的反對黨們先後八次提出對總統的不信任動議，南非的新聞調查記者們也挖掘出大量關於祖馬的「黑材料」，以類似維基解密形式的「Guptaleaks」方式將祖瑪和Gupta家族的黑材料全面公之於眾。一時間，南非輿論譁然，而祖瑪的下台也從此之後成為了必然，只是時間問題而已。</p>"},{"align":"center","title":"","src":"https://i.imgur.com/RYBwe62.png","credits":"","text":""}]}},{"videobackground":{"id":"7","format":{"fullpage":false},"title":"總統下台","subtitle":"<p>最後，在維護了祖瑪這麼多年之後，非洲最出名的百年政黨 ANC 不得不選擇做出切割，和他「劃清界線」，選擇黨內召回並要求他辭職。<br></p>","text":"","video":{"mp4":"uploads/default/zuma_resign.mp4","webm":""},"image":{"loading":""}}},{"textcentred":{"id":"8","title":"","files":["","",""],"subtitle":"","intro":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">credit :&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\">文字</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"> </span></b></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.jiemian.com/article/1837440.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">马里卡纳矿工之死：南非劳资冲突为何流血不止？</span></a></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">端傳媒:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 24px; color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20180222-notes-zuma-step-down/\" target=\"_blank\">祖瑪下台，南非十年政壇紙牌屋全劇終？</a></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px; color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">音樂:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 24px;\">South African National &nbsp;A</span><span style=\"color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 24px;\">nthem</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">照片:原拍攝者/新聞社</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><br></span></p>"}}],"nav":[{"id":0,"title":"前言"},{"id":1,"title":"從種族鬥爭到階級鬥爭"},{"id":2,"title":"利用左右方的 < > 觀看不同的照片"},{"id":3,"title":"上下移動的靜態照片 "},{"id":4,"title":"<p>激化的抗議&nbsp;</p>"},{"id":5,"title":"<p>總統的好朋友</p>"},{"id":6,"title":"<p>公民社會</p>"},{"id":7,"title":"總統下台"},{"id":8,"title":"8 textcentred"}]}